from PIL import Image, ImageChops, ImageFilter, ImageEnhance
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

# Load the original image
image_path = 'assets/HW_BodyXray2.png'
image = Image.open(image_path).convert('L')

# Display the original image
plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
plt.title('Original Image')
plt.imshow(image, cmap='gray')
plt.axis('off')
plt.show()
In[]:
# Step 1: Laplacian filter
laplacian_image = image.filter(ImageFilter.FIND_EDGES)

# Display the Laplacian filtered image
plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
plt.title('Step 1: Laplacian filter')
plt.imshow(laplacian_image, cmap='gray')
plt.axis('off')
plt.show()
In[]:
# Step 2: Sharpen the image by subtracting
sharpened_image = ImageChops.subtract(image, laplacian_image)

# Display the sharpened image
plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
plt.title('Step 2: Sharpened Image')
plt.imshow(sharpened_image, cmap='gray')
plt.axis('off')
plt.show()
In[]:
# Step 3: Apply Sobel filter (both x and y)
sobel_x = ImageFilter.Kernel(
    size=(3, 3),
    kernel=[-1, 0, 1, -2, 0, 2, -1, 0, 1],
    scale=1
)
sobel_y = ImageFilter.Kernel(
    size=(3, 3),
    kernel=[-1, -2, -1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 2, 1],
    scale=1
)

sobel_image_x = sharpened_image.filter(sobel_x)
sobel_image_y = sharpened_image.filter(sobel_y)
sobel_image = ImageChops.add(sobel_image_x, sobel_image_y)

# Display the Sobel filtered image
plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
plt.title('Step 3: Sobel Filtered Image')
plt.imshow(sobel_image, cmap='gray')
plt.axis('off')
plt.show()
In[]:
# Step 4: Combine Sobel filter
combined_image_d = ImageChops.add(sharpened_image, sobel_image)

# Display the combined image
plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
plt.title('Step 4: Combined Image')
plt.imshow(combined_image_d, cmap='gray')
plt.axis('off')
plt.show()
In[]:
# Step 5: Create a mask from the combined image and smoothed it
mask_image = ImageChops.multiply(combined_image_d, combined_image_d)

smoothed_image = mask_image.filter(ImageFilter.BoxBlur(2))
# Display the mask image
plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
plt.title('Step 5: Mask Image')
plt.imshow(smoothed_image, cmap='gray')
plt.axis('off')
plt.show()
In[]:
# Step 6: Sum the sharpened image with the smoothed mask
final_combined_image = ImageChops.add(sharpened_image, smoothed_image)

# Display the final combined image
plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
plt.title('Step 6: Final Combined Image')
plt.imshow(final_combined_image, cmap='gray')
plt.axis('off')
plt.show()
In[]:
# Step 7: Apply power-law transformation
gamma = 0.5
enhancer = ImageEnhance.Brightness(final_combined_image)
final_image_h = enhancer.enhance(gamma)

# Display the final enhanced image
plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
plt.title('Step 7: gamma Enhanced Image')
plt.imshow(final_image_h, cmap='gray')
plt.axis('off')
plt.show()
